Package: slasso
Type: Package
Title: Smooth LASSO Estimator for the Function-on-Function Linear Regression Model
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Fabio", "Centofanti", 
      email = "fabio.centofanti@unina.it", 
      role = c("cre","aut")),
    person("Antonio", "Lepore", role = c("aut")), 
    person("Simone", "Vantini", role = c("aut")), 
    person("Matteo", "Fontana", role = c("aut"))
    )
Description: Implements the S-LASSO (RoFANOVA), described in Centofanti et al. (2021) <arXiv:>. 
    It allows testing mean differences among groups of  functional data by being robust aginst the presence of outliers.
